{"tid":1300033,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（偽科普）特區政府史上一大迷思：法治","createTime":"2019-07-09T08:47:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T09:11:53.000Z","uid":263778,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c544f75996070af866ed030599b894c59d20f055","tid":1300033,"uid":263778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:47:40.000Z","msg":"利申，本人並非法律撚，不過中學時期聽過一個關於法治嘅講座，加上特區政府經常胡亂引用&ldquo;法治&rdquo;一詞，決定講下個人對法治嘅概念理解，歡迎法律撚糾正補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外我覺得好多人應該都唔清楚咩叫法治，尤其是中老年，所以大家可以隨意轉載，話比大家知其實政府一直都係9up緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">法治</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">英文Rule of Law</span></strong><br />\n主張<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">以法律作爲治理嘅依據</span></strong>，同&ldquo;人治&rdquo;係相反嘅概念<br />\n<br />\n法治有四個層次，分別係：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 有法可依</span></strong><br />\n即係你整一套法律出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">2. 有法必依</span></strong><br />\n即係你會跟住套法律做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">3. 以法限權</span></strong><br />\n即係你用法律平衡唔同行政機關嘅權力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">4. 以法達義</span></strong><br />\n即係用法律黎達到社會公義<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外值得一提，法治社會其中一個好重要嘅前提係<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">民主</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因爲立法需要有<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">民意授權</span></strong>，以一套完善嘅&ldquo;法律&rdquo;作爲民意嘅依據，作爲管治國家嘅最核心<br />\n因此除左要求<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>人民守法</strong></span>之外，政府亦好需要尊重法治中嘅<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>權力平衡</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁如果法律淪爲管治者嘅政治工具呢？<br />\n有一個好接近嘅用詞叫做<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Rule by Law</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>法制</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果政權凌駕法律，將佢變成管治工具，甚至侵犯公民權利，就會變成法制社會<br />\n而法制背後其實都係一種人治<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">所以！！！<br />\n一，如果唔係民主社會作爲前提，其實好難叫做法治社會；<br />\n二，好多人犯罪的確係有機會破壞法治；<br />\n三，但係政府唔遵守權力平衡都係一種破壞法治嘅行爲。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">法治係雙向架！！！雙向！！！！！</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">至於香港政府講嘅法治喎，大家聼下笑下就好啦...</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7623fdd2ed89ed627d6983b99fade3762f54ccc9","tid":1300033,"uid":263778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:49:22.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95b4646d0107472cea92baf053233c8339f16c5e","tid":1300033,"uid":227815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:50:31.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"a4d1b2292540a9c3b63916838fa2fe84eb9e2eb7","tid":1300033,"uid":262225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:52:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">我無嘢講 我要見律師</span>"},{"pid":"e67cb0df7fd481011e1d37de2bf00db5587654d4","tid":1300033,"uid":263778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:54:29.000Z","msg":"我要見律師JJ講法治<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01ef2cd192ab8bcd49d0c618e437d248869cdb16","tid":1300033,"uid":263778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:58:08.000Z","msg":"我要見律師JJ講法治<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f16bfe9cece5a4ff682f3e683fe235780dabfe1b","tid":1300033,"uid":230609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:59:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92016520c8830b9c285d78db551243ae6616299e","tid":1300033,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T09:00:07.000Z","msg":"認同請分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19bebc82bc9b79b7f8250444db1275ff5120436d","tid":1300033,"uid":112078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T09:00:23.000Z","msg":"從Norman Conquest同講起 比多啲人了解一下成個發展<br />\n另外Magna Carta一定要講"},{"pid":"c25f4d27c1a17d966c41a419b0fd3cda0098e322","tid":1300033,"uid":137459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T09:00:50.000Z","msg":"《一日爭取唔到真普選，我地永遠處於被動》<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1299151\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1299151</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7245084ee73a913c5fc69b623160b8c0ca7a4f5f","tid":1300033,"uid":16217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T09:01:47.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"dd28c7f47c7802e2c7ab7fc36fa33e3dd4bf263b","tid":1300033,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T09:08:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ddc3cd7cae55e51f99757c2bc24953c67f4997b","tid":1300033,"uid":183344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T09:11:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KCDhQFb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKCDhQFb.gif&h=8248cf26&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}